---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Moleculytics – AI Roadmap for Pharma & Life Science Graduates" showHeader={false} showFooter={false}>
  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 1 — COVER
  ══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="cover">
      <div class="cover-top">
        <img src="/Moleculytics My brand.png" class="cover-logo" alt="Moleculytics" />
        <div class="cover-badge">Free Resource · 2026 Edition</div>
        <div class="cover-title">
          The AI Roadmap for<br /><span>Pharma & Life Science</span><br />Graduates
        </div>
        <div class="cover-subtitle">
          Your step-by-step guide to entering the world of AI-powered drug discovery.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-hero">
        <div class="hero-pill">
          <div class="hero-pill-icon">🧬</div>
          <div class="hero-pill-text">
            <strong>No Coding Background?</strong>
            <span>You're in the right place</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-pill">
          <div class="hero-pill-icon">🇮🇳</div>
          <div class="hero-pill-text">
            <strong>Made for India</strong>
            <span>Pharma & Life Science focus</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-pill">
          <div class="hero-pill-icon">🚀</div>
          <div class="hero-pill-text">
            <strong>Career-Ready</strong>
            <span>Industry-aligned skills</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-inside">
        <h3>What's inside this guide</h3>
        <div class="inside-grid">
          <div class="inside-item">Why AI matters for your Pharma career</div>
          <div class="inside-item">Key AI skills needed in the industry</div>
          <div class="inside-item">AI coding tools — write code in plain English</div>
          <div class="inside-item">Myths that are holding you back — busted</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-footer">
        <span>© 2026 Moleculytics. All rights reserved.</span>
        <span class="brand">moleculytics.in</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 2 — WHY AI & MYTHS
  ══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="inner-page">
      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="page-header-left">
          <div class="page-header-icon">🧭</div>
          <div>
            <div class="page-header-title">The AI Opportunity</div>
            <div class="page-header-sub">Why AI is transforming the pharmaceutical sector in India</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/Moleculytics My brand.png" class="page-header-logo" alt="Moleculytics" style="max-width: 140px;" />
      </div>

      <div class="page-body-compact">
        <div class="section-label">Section 1</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Why Pharma Graduates Must Learn <span>AI Now</span></h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          The traditional drug discovery process takes 10–12 years and costs over $2.6 billion. AI models are shortening target identification times from years to weeks, predicting toxicities instantly, and designing entirely new molecules. Pharma companies in India (Biocon, Dr. Reddy's, Syngene, etc.) are actively building computational teams.
        </p>

        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-number">40%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Estimated cost reduction in early-stage discovery</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-number">2027</div>
            <div class="stat-label">The year AI skills become mandatory for R&amp;D roles</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-number">10x</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Increase in molecular datasets generated annually</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-header">
            <div class="info-card-icon">⚡</div>
            <div class="info-card-title">The Career Advantage</div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card-body">
            Pharma graduates with AI literacy are commanding **30% to 50% higher starting salaries** in India. They act as "translators" who bridge the gap between computer science and biology.
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:var(--navy);margin:16px 0 8px;">Busting Common AI Myths</h3>
        <div class="myth-row">
          <div class="myth-card">
            <div class="myth-left">
              <div class="myth-label">Myth #1</div>
              <div class="myth-text">"I need an engineering or advanced math degree to work with AI."</div>
            </div>
            <div class="myth-right">
              <div class="myth-label">Reality</div>
              <div class="myth-text">Modern tools focus on application. If you understand molecular structure, you can guide AI.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="myth-card">
            <div class="myth-left">
              <div class="myth-label">Myth #2</div>
              <div class="myth-text">"AI will fully replace scientists in R&amp;D."</div>
            </div>
            <div class="myth-right">
              <div class="myth-label">Reality</div>
              <div class="myth-text">AI won't replace scientists, but scientists who use AI **will replace** those who don't.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-footer">
        <span class="page-footer-brand">MOLECULYTICS</span>
        <span class="page-footer-page">Page 2 of 5</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 3 — SKILLS & CAREERS
  ══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="inner-page">
      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="page-header-left">
          <div class="page-header-icon">🛠️</div>
          <div>
            <div class="page-header-title">Skills &amp; Career Paths</div>
            <div class="page-header-sub">The concrete path to transitioning into AI × Pharma</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/Moleculytics My brand.png" class="page-header-logo" alt="Moleculytics" style="max-width: 140px;" />
      </div>

      <div class="page-body">
        <div class="section-label">Section 2</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Core Skills &amp; Career <span>Opportunities</span></h2>
        <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          Transitioning doesn't mean starting over. It means overlaying basic computational skills on top of your existing pharmacy, chemistry, or biotech knowledge.
        </p>

        <div class="skill-grid">
          <div class="skill-card teal">
            <span class="skill-emoji">🐍</span>
            <div class="skill-name">Scientific Python</div>
            <ul class="skill-list">
              <li>Variables &amp; Loops</li>
              <li>Data Structures (Lists, Dicts)</li>
              <li>Pandas (data handling)</li>
              <li>Data Visualization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-card pink">
            <span class="skill-emoji">🧪</span>
            <div class="skill-name">Cheminformatics</div>
            <ul class="skill-list">
              <li>RDKit libraries</li>
              <li>SMILES, InChI structures</li>
              <li>Fingerprints &amp; Similarity</li>
              <li>3D Conformations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-card navy">
            <span class="skill-emoji">🤖</span>
            <div class="skill-name">Molecular ML</div>
            <ul class="skill-list">
              <li>QSAR Model Building</li>
              <li>ADMET Predictions</li>
              <li>Feature Engineering</li>
              <li>Model Validation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-card green">
            <span class="skill-emoji">🧬</span>
            <div class="skill-name">Structural AI</div>
            <ul class="skill-list">
              <li>Protein-Ligand Docking</li>
              <li>AlphaFold confidence</li>
              <li>PDB structural parsing</li>
              <li>Active Site mapping</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:10px;">Hot Career Roles in India</h3>
        <div class="career-grid">
          <div class="career-card c1">
            <span class="career-icon">💻</span>
            <div class="career-title">Cheminformatics Associate</div>
            <div class="career-pay">₹6L - ₹10L/yr</div>
          </div>
          <div class="career-card c2">
            <span class="career-icon">🧪</span>
            <div class="career-title">Computational Toxicologist</div>
            <div class="career-pay">₹8L - ₹12L/yr</div>
          </div>
          <div class="career-card c3">
            <span class="career-icon">🧠</span>
            <div class="career-title">Molecular ML Engineer</div>
            <div class="career-pay">₹10L - ₹18L/yr</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-footer">
        <span class="page-footer-brand">MOLECULYTICS</span>
        <span class="page-footer-page">Page 3 of 5</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 4 — LEARNING PATH & SHORTCUTS
  ══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="inner-page">
      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="page-header-left">
          <div class="page-header-icon">📈</div>
          <div>
            <div class="page-header-title">The Learning Path</div>
            <div class="page-header-sub">Your step-by-step master plan to learning molecular AI</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/Moleculytics My brand.png" class="page-header-logo" alt="Moleculytics" style="max-width: 140px;" />
      </div>

      <div class="page-body">
        <div class="section-label">Section 3</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Step-by-Step Learning <span>Path</span></h2>
        
        <div class="roadmap">
          <div class="roadmap-step" data-num="1">
            <div class="step-phase">Phase 1 · 0 to 4 Weeks</div>
            <div class="step-title">Fundamentals of Scientific Python</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Learn how to read data, write loops, and work with numerical arrays. Skip general web design Python.</div>
            <div class="step-tags">
              <span class="tag">Python</span>
              <span class="tag navy">Pandas</span>
              <span class="tag green">Jupyter</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap-step" data-num="2">
            <div class="step-phase">Phase 2 · 5 to 8 Weeks</div>
            <div class="step-title">Represent Chemistry as Code</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Use RDKit to parse chemical structures, calculate descriptors, and run similarity searches.</div>
            <div class="step-tags">
              <span class="tag pink">RDKit</span>
              <span class="tag">SMILES</span>
              <span class="tag navy">Molecular Descriptors</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap-step" data-num="3">
            <div class="step-phase">Phase 3 · 9 to 12 Weeks</div>
            <div class="step-title">Machine Learning &amp; QSAR</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Train models to predict whether a molecule will bind to a target or have toxic properties.</div>
            <div class="step-tags">
              <span class="tag green">Scikit-Learn</span>
              <span class="tag pink">QSAR</span>
              <span class="tag">Random Forests</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          <span class="quote-mark">“</span>
          <h3>The AI Coding Shortcut</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:12px;">
            You no longer need to write boilerplate code from scratch. Modern AI coding assistants handle the syntax. Your job is to guide them using molecular logic.
          </p>

          <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;position:relative;">
            <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 12px;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#00BCD4;margin-bottom:4px;">OpenAI Codex</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.4;">Generates Python code directly from plain English prompts.</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 12px;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FF4DB8;margin-bottom:4px;">Claude Code</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.4;">Writes clean, annotated scripts with scientific context.</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 12px;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4CAF50;margin-bottom:4px;">Antigravity (Google)</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.4;">Agentic AI that plans, writes, and debugs full pipelines.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top:10px;padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(0,188,212,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,188,212,0.25);border-radius:8px;font-size:11.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);position:relative;">
            💡 <strong style="color:#00BCD4;">Moleculytics Tip:</strong> Learn faster by asking AI to explain code line-by-line rather than starting from scratch.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-footer">
        <span class="page-footer-brand">MOLECULYTICS</span>
        <span class="page-footer-page">Page 4 of 5</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 5 — CTA
  ══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="cta-page">
      <img src="/Moleculytics My brand.png" class="cta-logo" alt="Moleculytics" style="max-width: 200px;" />
      <div class="cta-label">Your Next Step</div>
      <div class="cta-title">
        Ready to Start Your<br /><span>AI × Pharma Journey?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-desc">
        Moleculytics is building India's most practical AI curriculum for Pharma and Life Science graduates. No jargon.
        No gatekeeping. Just real skills for real careers.
      </div>

      <div class="cta-steps">
        <div class="cta-step">
          <div class="cta-step-num">1</div>
          <div class="cta-step-text">
            <strong>Follow Moleculytics on LinkedIn</strong>
            <span>Get weekly AI × Pharma insights, tutorials, and tips — posted every week</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-step">
          <div class="cta-step-num">2</div>
          <div class="cta-step-text">
            <strong>📋 Fill in Our Interest Form — It Takes 2 Minutes</strong>
            <span>Tell us about your background so we can tailor what we build for you →
              <a href="https://forms.gle/ZGMrf2sWeRbbn6Mg8"
                style="color:#00BCD4;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline;">Click here to fill the form</a>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-divider"></div>

      <div class="cta-footer-text">
        © 2026 <strong>Moleculytics</strong> · AI Education for Pharma &amp; Life Science Professionals &amp; Students in India · Page 5 of 5<br />
        All rights reserved · moleculytics.in
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ─── RESET & BASE ─── */
  :root {
    --navy: #1A2B6B;
    --teal: #0097A7;
    --teal2: #00BCD4;
    --pink: #E91E8C;
    --pink2: #FF4DB8;
    --green: #4CAF50;
    --light: #F0FAFC;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --gray: #64748B;
    --gray-lt: #F1F5F9;
    --dark: #0D1B4B;
  }

  body {
    background: #e8edf5 !important;
    color: #1e293b !important;
  }

  .page {
    width: 794px;
    height: 1123px;
    background: white;
    margin: 32px auto;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    page-break-after: always;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 1 — COVER
  ══════════════════════════════════════ */
  .cover {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--dark) 0%, var(--navy) 50%, #1e3a8a 100%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 52px 60px 48px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* decorative circles */
  .cover::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px;
    right: -120px;
    width: 420px;
    height: 420px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .cover::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px;
    left: -80px;
    width: 360px;
    height: 360px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(233, 30, 140, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .cover-top {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cover-logo {
    height: 140px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cover-badge {
    background: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.5);
    color: var(--teal2);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .cover-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .cover-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal2), var(--pink2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .cover-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 520px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  /* hero visual */
  .cover-hero {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-pill {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 18px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .hero-pill-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
  }

  .hero-pill-text strong {
    display: block;
    color: white;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-pill-text span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  /* what's inside */
  .cover-inside {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px 36px;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cover-inside h3 {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal2);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .inside-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .inside-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .inside-item::before {
    content: '✓';
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--teal2));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cover-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 2;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  .cover-footer span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .cover-footer .brand {
    color: var(--teal2);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════════════
     INNER PAGE SHARED STYLES
  ══════════════════════════════════════ */
  .inner-page {
    height: 100%;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
    padding: 28px 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .page-header-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .page-header-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
  }

  .page-header-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
  }

  .page-header-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .page-header-logo {
    height: 52px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .page-body {
    padding: 44px 52px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .page-body-compact {
    padding: 20px 52px 24px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e0f7fa, #e8f5e9);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--teal);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .section-heading span {
    color: var(--pink);
  }

  .section-intro {
